                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <colophon xml:lang="gez" xml:id="coloph1">
                                <locus target="#154r"/>
                                ተፈጸመ፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ተአምሪሁ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ወአምላክነ፡ ወመድኃኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። አመ፡ ፩ለወርኃ፡ መጋቢት፡ ጊዜ፡ ፯ሰዓት፡ ዕለተ፡ ሐሙስ ፤ 
                                በ<date calendar="world" when="1715" when-custom="7207">፸፻፡
                                ወ፪፻ወ፯ዓመተ፡ ዓለም፡</date> በ<date calendar="evangelists">ዘመነ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ወንጌላዊ።</date> 
                               <subst>
                           <del rend="erasure"/>
                           <add place="overstrike">፫ተ፡</add>
                        </subst> ዓመተ፡ መንግሥቶመ፡
                                ለንጉሥነ፡ 
                               <subst> 
                           <del rend="erasure">
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10473Yostos">ዮስጦስ፤</persName>
                           </del>
                                <add place="overstrike">
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3430DawitII">ዳዊት፤</persName>
                           </add>
                        </subst> ሣህሉ፡ ወምሕረቱ፡ ይኩን፡ ላዕሌነ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                            </colophon>
                            <note>The miracles are numbered as 42 in the manuscript.</note>
